IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User jvshahid@gmail.com
PassCmd ~/bin/read-password-emacs
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs Login
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Maildir/gmail/
Inbox ~/Maildir/gmail/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim
AltMap yes

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge Slave
ExpireUnread yes
SyncState *
